config R8127
	tristate "RealTek RTL-8127 PCI 10 Gigabit Ethernet Adapter support"
	depends on PCI
	help
	  This is a driver for the 10 Gigabit Ethernet PCI network cards based on
	  the RTL-8127 chips. If you have one of those, say Y here.

	  To compile this driver as a module, choose M here: the module
	  will be called r8127. This is recommended.

